fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.mapping

Interface ManyValueWithArrays

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ManyValueMapper, ValueMapper

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface ManyValueWithArrays
extends ManyValueMapper
    A ManyValueMapper that provides a default behavior to represent the "multi-valued" characteristic as Object[].
